nodes.text: A cavernous warehouse that contained medical supplies was tended by an elderly man on the planet Vulta. Smuggler Zeerid Korr purchased a hoverchair for his crippled daughter, Arra Yooms, from the man at the warehouse in the year 3653 BBY.
The warehouse first appeared in the 2011 novel The Old Republic: Deceived, written by Paul S. Kemp.
